Something smells a little fishy in this new update…

Wait! Of course! Diggy’s discovered the brand new episode, Octo Park! Not only that, his buddy, Pink Hi, has dropped by to help guide you through the tenta-licious NEW LEVELS.

Be sure to update to the latest version for the most Sparktacular content!

We hear you wanted NEW LEVELS, so we’ve got 15 of them in this new update!

Head to Coral Utopia where you’ll be greeted by Lala Light, Diggy’s very fishy partner in crime. There are twists and turns aplenty so be sure bring your A-game!

Be sure to update to the latest version for all the new content!
